/money-heist-korea-joint-economic-area"><em>《韩国</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/money-heist-korea-joint-economic-area"><em>金钱抢劫</em></a>》）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/super-junior">Super Junior 的</a>崔始源、 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/woori-the-virgin">Woori The Virgin 的</a></em>成勋等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/parasite-park-so-dam-battle-with-cancer-i-cried-every-day-3557703">《寄生虫》女演员朴素丹讲述她与癌症的斗争：“我每天都哭”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
